l method to choose\nthe coarse-grainings most compatible with a specified Hamiltonian, which\nexhibit emergent classicality in the reduced state space. We apply this\nconstruction to the concrete example of the 1-D Ising model. Our results have\nrelevance for quantum information, bulk reconstruction in holography, and\nquantum gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-09"}
