,\ndistinct from other astrophysical contributions, could be distinguishable\nsignatures for these exotic monopole states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 18:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 19:30:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
