itative evaluations and\nalso presented comparisons with several state-of-art models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Sep 2019 05:36:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Oct 2019 01:56:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-07"}
